  "description": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Helvetica\",sans-serif;color:#585858'>Ce\njeu de données, rafraichi une fois par jour, présente les signaux écogaz au\npérimètre France (hors Corse) sur 5 jours. Ainsi, il présente les derniers\nsignaux écogaz publiés.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Helvetica\",sans-serif;\ncolor:#585858'>Le dispositif écogaz est exclusivement national.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Helvetica\",sans-serif;\ncolor:#585858'>Le signal est disponible sur le site Open Data Réseaux Energies. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Helvetica\",sans-serif;\ncolor:#585858'>Pour chacune des périodes de la journée sont associés une valeur\net un texte. La valeur est représenté par une couleur. La signification des\nvaleurs est la suivante :<o:p></o:p></span></p><ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(88, 88, 88); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Helvetica\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\n     \"Times New Roman\"'>Vert </span><span style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\n     \"Helvetica\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\n     color:black'>(1)</span><span style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Helvetica\",sans-serif;\n     mso-fareast-font-family:\"Times New Roman\"'>: Notre consommation est\n     raisonnable.</span><span style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"inherit\",serif;\n     mso-fareast-font-family:\"Times New Roman\"'><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(88, 88, 88); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Helvetica\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\n     \"Times New Roman\"'>Jaune </span><span style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\n     \"Helvetica\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\n     color:black'>(2)</span><span style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Helvetica\",sans-serif;\n     mso-fareast-font-family:\"Times New Roman\"'>: Notre consommation est\n     élevée. Une modération de la consommation est bienvenue.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(88, 88, 88); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Helvetica\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\n     \"Times New Roman\"'>Orange </span><span style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\n     \"Helvetica\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\n     color:black'>(3)</span><span style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Helvetica\",sans-serif;\n     mso-fareast-font-family:\"Times New Roman\"'>: Le réseau de gaz est dans une\n     situation tendue. En adaptant sa consommation, chacun peut\n     contribuer à l’effort collectif et éviter que des grands consommateurs ne soient\n     mis à contribution par une baisse importante de leur consommation.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(88, 88, 88); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Helvetica\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\n     \"Times New Roman\"'>Rouge </span><span style='font-size:10.5pt;\n     font-family:\"Helvetica\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\n     color:black'>(4)</span><span style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Helvetica\",sans-serif;\n     mso-fareast-font-family:\"Times New Roman\"'>: Le réseau de gaz est dans une\n     situation très tendue. Des ordres de délestage pourraient être envoyés très\n     prochainement aux acteurs concernés. Réduisons tous notre consommation\n     pour permettre un retour à une situation normale le plus rapidement\n     possible.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n</ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Helvetica\",sans-serif;\ncolor:#585858'>Toutes les infos sur</span><span style='font-size:10.5pt;\nfont-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;color:#585858'><a href=\"https://myecogaz.com\" target=\"_blank\"> </a></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(88, 88, 88);\"><a href=\"https://myecogaz.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://</a></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(88, 88, 88);\"><a href=\"https://myecogaz.com/\" target=\"_blank\">myecogaz.com</a></span></p><p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Helvetica\",sans-serif;\ncolor:#585858'>Les données de la journée courante, jusque J+5 sont accessibles\nen temps réel sur le site<a href=\"https://myecogaz.com\"> </a></span><span style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\n\"Arial\",sans-serif;color:#585858'><a href=\"https://myecogaz.com\">Ecogaz</a></span><span style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Helvetica\",sans-serif;color:#585858'> (</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(88, 88, 88);\"><a href=\"https://myecogaz.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://</a></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(88, 88, 88);\"><a href=\"https://myecogaz.com/\" target=\"_blank\">myecogaz.com</a></span><span style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Helvetica\",sans-serif;color:#585858'>) et peuvent\névoluer d’une journée sur l’autre selon la situation de l’équilibre\noffre-demande, des situations de tension et de la prévision\nde consommation au niveau national. La mise à jour de l’indicateur se\nfait aux alentours de 11h</span><span style=\"color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt;\">.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font color=\"#585858\" face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\">Une question sur ces données ? n'hésitez pas à utiliser notre <a href=\"https://odre.opendatasoft.com/pages/contactv2/\" target=\"_blank\">formulaire de contact</a></font></p>",
